entry.title: U.S. to Return Embassy to Ukraine, Boost Military Aid
entry.content: The U.S. will return an embassy presence to Ukraine and increase military support for the country, Secretary of State Antony Blinken and Defense Secretary Lloyd Austin told Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky during a meeting in Kyiv.

entry.title: France's Macron Wins Second Term
entry.content: French President Emmanuel Macron was re-elected, according to projections based on early ballot counts, overcoming deep divisions among voters worried about inflation and immigration.
